{"title":"雪之歌","authors":["纪鹏"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":2,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪鹏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天的雪啊飘飘落下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银装素裹，玉树梨花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑞雪复盖着麦苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春来定是片好庄稼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地在召唤着犁头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种子急待破土发芽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社党委在讨论九中全会决议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队队都在架辕套马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花飘过牛棚马厩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一群健壮的耕牛大马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员们在检修犁头、耕具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕双肩落满雪花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万事俱备，备耕工作都已作好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像拉满弓的弦，一触即发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地不会辜负辛勤的汗水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间将献出丰收的庄稼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天的雪啊飘飘落下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人心里盛满朝霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到秋来万里长空飞捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定赛过这漫天的雪花。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}